Class SignatureIntegrityRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardtime.envelope.verification.rule.AbstractRule<SignatureContent>
      • com.guardtime.envelope.verification.rule.generic.SignatureIntegrityRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rule<SignatureContent>

    public class SignatureIntegrityRule
extends AbstractRule<SignatureContent>
    Rule that verifies the EnvelopeSignature of a SignatureContent by using a SignatureVerifier to verify the underlying signature. Will terminate verification upon non OK results.
